sp.p:
I'le coole my hot louer, he shall sit on a perch for a stale, now must I be vncupidate, & shortly appeare here Cosmafied, it shall be hard but with the same limetwig I'le catch a bigger bird then this.


First I will serue my selfe, my mistris after;

My baite is seeming loue, my prey true laughter.

